<div id="review_2286866981" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2286866981" />
    <a title="Larry  Loveday" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/72450443-larry-loveday"><img alt="Larry  Loveday" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1507757705p2/72450443.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2286866981?book_show_action=true">Feb 12, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Larry  Loveday" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Larry  Loveday" href="/user/show/72450443-larry-loveday">Larry  Loveday</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2286866981" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4301738349056349279"><strong>As good as the first</strong><br/><br/>I enjoyed this book almost as much as book one of The Grave Report. Vincent and Ortiz are such great characters, and they work so well together. Can&apos;t wait to see what happens in book three.</span>
  <span id="freeText4301738349056349279" style="display:none"><strong>As good as the first</strong><br /><br />I enjoyed this book almost as much as book one of The Grave Report. Vincent and Ortiz are such great characters, and they work so well together. Can't wait to see what happens in book three.</span>
  <a data-text-id="4301738349056349279" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
