              <span id="reviewTextContainer2616376977" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2683804867626338919"><strong>Vincent gets sent after a new type of monster.</strong><br/><br/>And meets up with Ortiz again. Mental institution with patients dying of what is said to be heart attacks. We as readers learn about phages. Keeps Vincent and Ortiz busy and us readers reading as fast as possible.<br/><br/>Read and enjoy!!!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


